README

This folder contains output logs of read counts from the RNA processing scripts. 

For each tree there is a log of:
#--------------------------------#
1. <Sample>_fastp.txt
Reads filtered from each sample during the fastp processing

2. Hisat-Alignment-Array<array_number>.out
Hisat mapping in for each tree. Sample is found in the first row of each file. 

There is also a summary of paired end reads remaining after sortmeRNA in rRNA_read_counts.txt
